      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GETTING CHEEKY (4) beaten last start over the 400m at this track but finished in the minors in a handy 22.78. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. MASTER KILCOY (2) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (23.07) at this track over 400m. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Overdue and is among the main hopes. BLACK WANDA (6) settled back but wound up strongly to score by 2.25 lengths (20.25) at Angle Park in TG1-4W. Is yet to find the frame here from six. Should feature again. CHEAT CODE (1) is not to be discarded.",
